'''Kevin Hanssen''', ni [[Zimbabwe|umukinnyi wa firime Zimbabwe]], umwanditsi akaba n'umucuranzi.  Azwi cyane kubera uruhare muri firime ''Mind Games'', ''Mugabe'' na ''The Telling Room'' . 

== Umwuga ==
Mu 1994, yabonye impamyabumenyi ya Bachelor of Arts muri UNISA, [[Afurika y'Epfo]].  Ni n'umunyamuryango washinze Over The Edge Theatre Company.  Yakinnye mu ikinamico 'A Man Like You' yakinwe mu makinamico menshi ya [[Zimbabwe]]. 

== Ibihembo ==
Yatsindiye ibihembo byinshi mu minsi mikuru mpuzamahanga. 

* BAT Umukinnyi mwiza ushyigikira - ''Ntabwo ndi Rappaport'' (1993)
* Tora igihembo cya Fringe, Iserukiramuco rya Edinburgh - ''Ijoro rya cumi na kabiri'' (2001)
* Umwuka wa Fringe Igihembo, Iserukiramuco rya Edinburgh - ''Yavutse Afurika'' (2003)
* BAT Igihembo Cyabakinnyi Cyiza - ''Miss Julie'' (2010)
* AFDIS Igihembo Cyabakinnyi Cyiza - ''Umugenzuzi Hamagara'' (2015)
* Igihembo cyumukinnyi mwiza, Iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya firime rya Zimbabwe - ''Imikino Yubwenge'' (2017)
* Igihembo cya AFDIS Umukinnyi mwiza - Umugore ''wanjye mwiza'' (2017)

